headline: FIS Premium Payback Aims to Enhance Savings and Convenience for Bilt Members
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., April 03, 2025--FIS® (NYSE: FIS), a global leader in financial technology, today announced that its Premium Payback solution has been chosen to power the real-time rewards redemption process for Bilt. Launched in 2021, Bilt is the pioneering payments and commerce network that transforms housing and neighborhood spending into rewards and benefits for everyone involved.
